The page displays a table with shipment information including shipment numbers, ship dates, order numbers, order dates, ship-to names, quantities, and actions. I can see that there are 4 shipments in the system:

2. Shipment #000000002 for John Doe (shipped Apr 19, 2023)
3. Shipment #000000003 for Grace Nguyen (shipped Apr 23, 2023)
4. Shipment #000000004 for John Lee (shipped Mar 23, 2025)
